There was a time when I would have wanted this - I was a python guy for years. But I&#x27;ve found I can be just as dynamic in scala (perhaps even more so, given implicits), without having to give up type safety. E.g. his example looks almost identical in scala:<p><pre><code>    List(&quot;Rob&quot;, &quot;Christopher&quot;, &quot;Joe&quot;, &quot;John&quot;).filter{ 
      _.size <= 4 
    }.foreach {
      println _
    }</code></pre>
